## Import
---
layout: false
class: middle

- Partials

  ```scss
  // _variables.scss
  $primary-color: #1a59b6;
  $bg-color: #ddd;
  $font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;
  ```

  ```scss
  // _reset.scss
  html,
  body,
  ul,
  ol {
     margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
  }
  ```

- Main stylesheet
  ```scss
  // style.scss
  @import 'variables';
  @import 'reset';

  body {
    font-family: $font-family;
    background: $bg-color;
  }

  h1 {
    color: $primary-color;
  }
  ```
